&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;üì∫ &lt;a href="https://javascriptweekly.com/link/179114/rss" style=" color: #3366aa; font-weight: 500 !important;   "&gt;The full set of React Conf 2025 videos&lt;/a&gt; is now online, made up of 25 talks and 23 interviews, including &lt;a href="https://javascriptweekly.com/link/179115/rss" style=" color: #3366aa; font-weight: 500 !important;   "&gt;one with four members of the core team.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
